Package me.masstrix.eternalnature.core.particle

Class BaseParticle

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.masstrix.eternalnature.core.particle.BaseParticle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EternalEntity, EternalParticle, Ticking
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LeafParticle
    public abstract class BaseParticle
extends java.lang.Object
implements Ticking, EternalParticle
    Base for custom particles. This stores the core attributes that would be needed for most particles and implements the base methods needed.

    It's recommended to use a ShadowEntity when creating particles so there are not issues with them becoming stuck in the world if using entities to create the effect.
